snippet: Worries about China’s military buildup in the Pacific will be high on the agenda as Defense Secretary Leon E. Panetta meets with Southeast Asian defense ministers in Indonesia.
lead_paragraph: Worries about China’s military buildup in the Pacific will be high on the agenda as Defense Secretary Leon E. Panetta meets with Southeast Asian defense ministers in Indonesia.
